title: Dave Matthews Band - Weekend On The Rocks
description:
This DVD is cut together from 3-day concert at the rocks!!!
This is a DVD that comes with the Weekend on the rocks 2 Disc + DVD combo. It is not a exclusive dvd release. But combined with a nice bottle of wine, it is sure nice though. Time of the season and Louisiana Bayou is to very nice DMB tracks!!!! Enjoy!!!!!!

Original Release Date: November 29, 2005
Number of Discs: 1
Format: Live
Label: RCA


Tracklist:
01. Stand Up (For It)
02. Time Of The Season
03. Dreamgirl
04. Everybody Wake Up (Our Finest Hour Arrives)
05. Crash Into Me
06. So Much To Say
07. Too Much
08. Louisiana Bayou
09. Recently
10. Jimi Thing
